PromoNBuying application is designed for capstone project.
The aim of designing this application is to provide free application so that anyone can add/launch the product or service with certian promotions with promotion start and end date.
There is customer comments area where customer can share their buying expereince so that others can take benefit from thier review to take necessary actions either to buy this product or not.
According to customer's comments product owners can enhance the features of the product or can change the promotions startegies according to the requirements.
Soon source code will be uploaded to this repository. 

PormoNBuying Development.
